data.description: You will love this country living on 10 acres in Geronimo but in Walters School District!  This brick home was built in 2013 and features 4 bedrooms and an office, 2.5 bathrooms, a 2 car garage and a storage room off the laundry room.  Great storage and closets throughout this home!  The living area features vinyl plank flooring and is open to the kitchen and dining area.  The kitchen has granite counters, stainless steel appliances, a nice breakfast bar and plenty of room for cooking.  The main bedroom is on one side of the home and is big enough for large furniture also has a tray ceiling.  The main bathroom has a double sink granite vanity, a makeup table, corner jacuzzi tub, a tiled spacious walk-in shower and a wonderful walk-in closet.  The kids rooms are all good size with great closet space.  The office has a tiled floor and is towards the back of home in case someone working from home needs privacy.  Updates - Air Handler 2022; Water Heater 2021; Dishwasher 2021; Microwave 2021.  Nice long covered front porch and a nice covered back patio.  There is a 40x40 barn and a 30x50 barn both with dirt floors.  Also outside is a nice little "she shed or man cave or guest quarters measuring about 600 square feet with electricity, water and a half bath.  The 10 acres is fenced with cross wire.  Perfect country living.  Owner has an additional 90 acres around the home and willing to negotiate a price for it all.
